instructions: Put the Plate on the Charger
Put the naplin on the plate
Put the fork to the left of the plate with prong pointing upward
Put the Salad Fork to the left of the fork with prong facing up
Put the Dinner Knife to the right of the plate with the blade pointing up
Put the tea spoon to the right of the dinner knife with bowl pointing up
Put the Soup Spoon to the right of the Tea Spoon with bowl facing up
Put the glass in top right of Charger
Place the wine glass to the right of the Water Glass
Place the Water glass below the wine glass
Place the coffee cup to the right of the wine glass
Place the bread plate to the top left of the Charger
Place the Butter Knife on top of the Bread Plate with blade facing right
Place the desert fork to the right of the Bread Plate with prong facing right
Place the desert spoon below the Desert fork with the bowl facing left
